{"title":"回忆秋天","authors":["汤锋"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":9,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"回忆秋天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汤锋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋天是父亲留下的一张犁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老黄牛是我的伴侣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吆喝和鞭声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为我的平原飞翔不息"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在季节的更替处，脊梁和犁尖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成为回忆的动人画面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜悦的果实，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是母亲挂在枝头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抑或梦中的爱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春去秋来，果实"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滑落于牛尾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"父亲长满粗茧的手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在牛蹄下辛勤撒播"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弯弯阡陌间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄昏不老黎明永远年轻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"许多年后回故土"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看见那张犁，便会忆起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶秋的牛和父亲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有母亲倚门吆喝黄昏的声音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}